
                INSTALL

To build this library from source, you need:

- ant
- ivy (you do not need ivy if you manually downloaded dependencies
  and set: ivy.resolved=true in common.properties file)

then type in directory with sources:

ant

the files should appear in dist directory.

Required libraries:

- implementation of StaX streaming appi (for ex. Woodstox)
- javassist


to run test you need also JUnit 4.x or later.
